Sentencas: In order to uncover the inner working mechanism and performance of solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) with biomass gasification syngas as fuel, a two dimensional SOFC multi-physical field model is established.
Titulo: Multi-physics field modeling of biomass gasification syngas fueled solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: This study makes up for the deficiency that the previous studies of coupling biomass gasification unit and SOFC stack mostly stay at the system level.
Titulo: Multi-physics field modeling of biomass gasification syngas fueled solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The results show that the SOFC fueled by the syngas produced from gasification of biomass with steam as the agent has the best performance.
Titulo: Multi-physics field modeling of biomass gasification syngas fueled solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The peak power density could achieve approximately 10240 W m- 2.
Titulo: Multi-physics field modeling of biomass gasification syngas fueled solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: With the improvement of operating temperature, the peak power density of SOFC will be increased.
Titulo: Multi-physics field modeling of biomass gasification syngas fueled solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: At the temperature of 1123 K, the peak power density could achieve about 15128 W m- 2.
Titulo: Multi-physics field modeling of biomass gasification syngas fueled solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: 3 s-1 when the operating temperature is 1123 K.
Titulo: Multi-physics field modeling of biomass gasification syngas fueled solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: This indicates that the WGS reaction will proceed in reverse direction at high temperatures, thereby reducing the hydrogen concentration.
Titulo: Multi-physics field modeling of biomass gasification syngas fueled solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In addition, increase in the anode flux and decrease in the cell length lead to the increase of SOFC current density.
Titulo: Multi-physics field modeling of biomass gasification syngas fueled solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In general, this work could provide guidance for the optimization and practical application of SOFC using biomass syngas as fuel.
Titulo: Multi-physics field modeling of biomass gasification syngas fueled solid oxide fuel cell
